<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann III. von Hohenzollern, Burggraf von Nürnberg</head><p>Der Rat teilt mit, dass die Judenschaft zu Nürnberg gemäß königlicher Anweisung den Austrag mit dem Adressaten vor Markgraf Friedrich I. von Brandenburg anstrebt und daher nicht aufsässig ist, bittet um Verständnis und verweist auf den Rechtsweg an den üblichen Gerichtsstätten.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_65" id="31v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_65_r1l3">Burggraf <expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_65_r1l4"><expan>Gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr <expan>Hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> yecʒ nehſt <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat . von der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l5"><expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns wonhaft etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l6">Nu als eẅr gnade in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> brıef meldt / es ſey wol <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wıe Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l7">dıe ſache mıt der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns gehandelt / Vnd wıe Jr <expan>dıeſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Juden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l8">in des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> Reıchs acht getan habt / ſölıch brıef durch dıe vnſern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l9">freuelıch <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>abgerıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeın etc Hoffen wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ſüll wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l10">eingedenk ſeın . wıe wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vormals <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> . ſölıch vnd <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l11">artıkel dıe ſache antreffend / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> notdurft <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurtt</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l12">mit <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brıef des <expan>datu<ex>m</ex></expan> hellt am montag vor ſand <expan>Margarete<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l13">tag <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> Darinn eẅr gnade vnd <expan>menıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l14">wır redlıch vnd <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch</expan> damıt <expan>vmbgange<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein / Denn als vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l15">eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade in <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>nehſte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>br<ex>ief</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat / vvıe wol vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l16">der <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> durchleẅchtıgıſt fürſt vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> <expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Sıgmund <expan>Römıſch<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l17">ʒu <expan>Vng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd ʒu Beheım etc künıg <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ſeıd <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> ʒeıt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l18"><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ernſtl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns daran ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l19">weıſen ſıch mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>rıchte<ex>n</ex></expan> / des Jr <expan>bıſh<ex>er</ex></expan> gewartt habt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l20">noch niht fındet daʒ ſıe keinrley gleıcheıt für ſıch nemen etc . Verſteen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l21">wir niht daʒ vns der <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der künıg . ver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l22"><expan>ſchrıbe<ex>n</ex></expan> oder <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu weıſen . <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> denn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l23">nach Jnnhalt vnd <expan>auſʒweıſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> ſeinr <expan>künıglıch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef vormals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l24"><expan>darüb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gegeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Des auch wır von der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l25"><expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Marggraf <expan>frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> durch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l26"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> rate . vnd dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> für ſıch ſelbs / ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l27"><expan>menig<ex>er</ex>m</expan> male fleıſſıg <expan>gebette<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dıe <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>n<ex>te</ex></expan> ſache <expan>ʒwıſch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_65_r1l28"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd der <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>entſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> nach lawt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_66" id="32r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l2"><expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künıgs brıef <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l3"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> geſant / Des wır <expan>hoffe<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ der <expan>vorg<ex>ena</ex>nt<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l4">Marggraf wol eingedenk ſülle ſein / So <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch dıe <expan>Jüdıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l5">vns / des vor <expan>demſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem <expan>Marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> noch alſo <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l6">awſʒtrag <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> Vnd wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> mıt fleıſſ darcʒu tun / Dabey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l7">eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> vnd <expan>menıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> mag / daʒ dıe <expan>Judıſch<ex>eit</ex></expan> bey vns niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l8"><expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>ſecʒıg</expan> noch <expan>vngehorſa<ex>m</ex></expan> vnd der ſache nach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l9">künıgs geheıſſ ʒu awſʒtrag ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> . nıht ſeẅmıg <expan>geweſe<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l10"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒogen</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd auch noch nıht ſeẅmıg ſein noch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒıehen</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l11">Deẅht aber eẅr <expan>furſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade / daʒ wır in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> ıcht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> getan <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r2l12"><expan>gelaſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan> . denn wır pılleıch <expan>ſölte<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Daru<ex>n</ex>b</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
